    PassageItemIndex: 0,
    Passage: null,
    PassageTitle: null,
    IsLinkedQuestion: null,
    Points: 3,
    NegativePoints: 1,
    Explanation:
      "<p class=\"expans\">The median rank in the class will be 3 since there are 5 students.</p>\n<p class=\"expans\">C has a better rank than the median rank. Therefore, C's rank is either 1 or 2.</p>\n<p>B got higher marks than C. Therefore, B's rank will be 1.</p>\n<p>D got a higher score than E.</p>\n<p>D's rank will be either 3 or 4.</p>\n<p>Hence, E's rank will be either 4 or 5 and A's rank will be either 3 or 4 or 5.</p>\n<p>The 3 possible arrangements from left to right are AEDCB; EADCB or EDACB.</p>\n<p>Hence, [2].</p>",
